oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Kayne Avenue Missonary Baptist Church, c.1970s
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the new Kayne Avenue Missionary Baptist Church. The congregation was originally founded in 1886, and the congregation built this church at 1025 12th Avenue South in 1973. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
